{
  "chapter": "第三章：代数之美——椭圆标准方程的构建",
  "scenes": [
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "thinking"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "化简到这一步，出现了 a²−c²。因为它始终大于 0，我们不妨给它起个新名字。观察黑板上的直角三角形，你能找到它对应的线段吗？"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/triangle_pof2.svg"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s07_quiz",
      "tts_text": "化简到这一步，出现了 a的平方减c的平方。因为它始终大于 0，我们不妨给它起个新名字。观察黑板上的直角三角形，你能找到它对应的线段吗？"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_quiz",
      "type": "choice",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "thinking"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "当 P 在短轴顶点时，a 对应 PF₂，c 对应 OF₂，那么 √(a²−c²) 对应的线段是？"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/triangle_pof2.svg"
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "A. PF₂",
          "correct": false,
          "next": "ch03_s07_wrong"
        },
        {
          "text": "B. OF₂",
          "correct": false,
          "next": "ch03_s07_wrong"
        },
        {
          "text": "C. OP（短轴半长）",
          "correct": true,
          "next": "ch03_s07_correct",
          "scoreChange": 10
        }
      ],
      "tts_text": "当 P 在短轴顶点时，a 对应 P F2，c 对应 O F2，那么根号下a的平方减c的平方对应的线段是？"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_correct",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "happy",
        "action": "bounce"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "没错！根据勾股定理，我们令 b = √(a²−c²)，即 b² = a²−c²。"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "math",
        "content": "b = \\sqrt{a^2 - c^2}, \\quad b^2 = a^2 - c^2"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s07_substitute",
      "tts_text": "没错！根据勾股定理，我们令 b 等于根号下a的平方减c的平方，即 b的平方等于a的平方减c的平方。"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_substitute",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "excited"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "把 b² = a²−c² 代入方程，两边同除以 a²b²，看看会发生什么！"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/derivation_final.svg"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s08_reveal",
      "tts_text": "把 b的平方等于a的平方减c的平方代入方程，两边同除以 a的平方乘b的平方，看看会发生什么！"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s07_wrong",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "sad",
        "action": "shake"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "再想想，当 P 在短轴顶点时，△POF₂ 是直角三角形，OP 是一条直角边，用勾股定理算算看？"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/triangle_pof2.svg"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s07_quiz",
      "tts_text": "再想想，当 P 在短轴顶点时，三角形 P O F2 是直角三角形，O P 是一条直角边，用勾股定理算算看？"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_reveal",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "excited"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "把 b² = a²−c² 代入方程，两边同除以 a²b²，就得到了一个漂亮的方程！"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/derivation_final.svg"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s08_explain",
      "tts_text": "把 b的平方等于a的平方减c的平方代入方程，两边同除以 a的平方乘b的平方，就得到了一个漂亮的方程！"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_explain",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "happy"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "这就是焦点在 x 轴上的椭圆标准方程！它不仅对称、简洁，还充满和谐的美感。"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "math",
        "content": "\\frac{x^2}{a^2} + \\frac{y^2}{b^2} = 1 \\quad (a > b > 0)"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s08_transition"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_transition",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "thinking"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "那么，如果焦点跑到了 y 轴上呢？通过类比推导，方程会变成什么样？让我们做个实验观察一下。"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "math",
        "content": "\\frac{x^2}{a^2} + \\frac{y^2}{b^2} = 1 \\quad (a > b > 0)"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s08_lab"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_lab",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "excited"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "滑动滑块，观察焦点在不同轴上时，分母的大小关系有什么规律？"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "lab",
        "labType": "lab-classify"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s08_quiz"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_quiz",
      "type": "choice",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "thinking"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "观察发现，当焦点在 x 轴时，x² 下的分母较____；当焦点在 y 轴时，y² 下的分母较____。"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "lab",
        "labType": "lab-classify"
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "A. 较小；较大",
          "correct": false,
          "next": "ch03_s08_wrong"
        },
        {
          "text": "B. 较大；较大",
          "correct": true,
          "next": "ch03_s08_correct",
          "scoreChange": 10
        }
      ],
      "tts_text": "观察发现，当焦点在 x 轴时，x的平方下的分母较什么；当焦点在 y 轴时，y的平方下的分母较什么。"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_correct",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "happy",
        "action": "bounce"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "记住了，谁的分母大，焦点就在谁的轴上！"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/standard_eq_forms.svg"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s08_abc_quiz"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_wrong",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "sad",
        "action": "shake"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "再仔细看看实验，焦点所在的轴对应的分母一定是更大的那个哦！"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "lab",
        "labType": "lab-classify"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s08_quiz"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_abc_quiz",
      "type": "choice",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "thinking"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "观察实验数值，无论椭圆的焦点在 x 轴还是 y 轴上，长半轴、短半轴和半焦距之间都满足什么关系？"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "lab",
        "labType": "lab-classify"
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "A.（长半轴）²=（短半轴）²+（半焦距）²",
          "correct": true,
          "next": "ch03_s08_abc_correct",
          "scoreChange": 10
        },
        {
          "text": "B.（半焦距）²=（短半轴）²+（长半轴）²",
          "correct": false,
          "next": "ch03_s08_abc_wrong"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_abc_correct",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "happy",
        "action": "bounce"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "没错！无论焦点在哪个轴上，都有（长半轴）²=（短半轴）²+（半焦距）²，即 a² = b² + c²。记住这个关系，后面会经常用到！"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "lab",
        "labType": "lab-classify"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s09_intro",
      "tts_text": "没错！无论焦点在哪个轴上，都有长半轴的平方等于短半轴的平方加半焦距的平方，即 a的平方等于b的平方加c的平方。记住这个关系，后面会经常用到！"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s08_abc_wrong",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "sad",
        "action": "shake"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "再看看实验中的数值，长半轴是最大的那个，它和短半轴、半焦距之间的关系类似勾股定理哦！"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "lab",
        "labType": "lab-classify"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s08_abc_quiz"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s09_intro",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "excited"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "恭喜！你已经完成了本次探秘。从圆锥的切割，到拉绳实验，再到现在的代数方程。我们一起总结一下吧。"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/summary.svg"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s09_summary"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s09_summary",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "normal"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "圆锥曲线包含椭圆、双曲线、抛物线和圆。而我们推导出的椭圆标准方程有两种形式。来做最后一道检验题！"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/standard_eq_axes.svg"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s09_quiz"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s09_quiz",
      "type": "choice",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "thinking"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "以下哪个是椭圆的标准方程，并且焦点位置表述正确？"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/standard_eq_axes.svg"
      },
      "options": [
        {
          "text": "A. x²/a² + y²/b² = 1 (a>b>0)，焦点在 x 轴",
          "correct": true,
          "next": "ch03_s09_correct",
          "scoreChange": 10
        },
        {
          "text": "B. x²/a² + y²/b² = 1 (b>a>0)，焦点在 x 轴",
          "correct": false,
          "next": "ch03_s09_wrong"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s09_correct",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "happy",
        "action": "bounce"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "完美！记住，AB 两种形式都是椭圆标准方程，只是焦点位置不同。a 永远是较大的那个分母的根！"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/standard_eq_forms.svg"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s09_end"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s09_wrong",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "sad",
        "action": "shake"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "注意哦，椭圆的焦点是在x轴上还是在y轴上取决于椭圆方程中是含x项的分母大还是含y项的分母大"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/standard_eq_axes.svg"
      },
      "next": "ch03_s09_quiz"
    },
    {
      "id": "ch03_s09_end",
      "type": "dialogue",
      "mambo": {
        "expression": "excited"
      },
      "dialogue": {
        "text": "下次探险，我们将深入研究椭圆的几何性质。坐标法是我们的纽带，数学之美永不止步。再见啦！"
      },
      "blackboard": {
        "type": "image",
        "src": "/labimage/ch03/ending.svg"
      },
      "next": null
    }
  ]
